title: Durable Oppo A6 Pro is official with 7,000mAh battery and new antenna
summary: The Oppo A6 Pro is official, and it's one tough smartphone. Rated for IP66, IP68, and IP69, it can handle 8,000KPa of hot water pressure, can soak in 1.5 meters of water for half an hour, and can be used with wet or oily hands.
